# Conducty Repo Conventions

- Skills live in `skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md` and follow the Cursor skill format with `name` and `description` frontmatter
- Subagent prompt templates live alongside their skill as `<role>-prompt.md` (e.g. `implementer-prompt.md`)
- Installable rules live in `rules/*.mdc` with standard Cursor rule frontmatter
- Keep SKILL.md files under 500 lines; keep rules under 50 lines
- Use `~/.conducty/` as the persistent state directory (plans, history, context, designs)
- Daily plans use the template in `skills/conducty-plan/daily-plan-template.md`
- All file paths in skills should use POSIX format (forward slashes, ~ for home)
